### Get all budgets for current logged in user
GET http://localhost:3000/api/budgets/
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### post new Budget
# @name postNewBudget
POST http://localhost:3000/api/budgets/
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

